tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE weightlifting_equipment ( 
    equipment_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    equipment_name VARCHAR(50), 
    equipment_type VARCHAR(50), 
    quantity INT, 
    weight DECIMAL(10,2), 
    availability BOOLEAN 
);

CREATE TABLE barbells (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    brand VARCHAR(50),
    weight INT,
    material VARCHAR(50),
    quantity INT
);

CREATE TABLE plates (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    weight INT,
    color VARCHAR(20),
    quantity INT,
    barbell_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (barbell_id) REFERENCES barbells(id)
);

CREATE TABLE barbells (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    brand VARCHAR(50),
    weight DECIMAL,
    material VARCHAR(50),
    condition VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE plates (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    weight DECIMAL,
    color VARCHAR(50),
    quantity INT,
    material VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE collars (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    brand VARCHAR(50),
    type VARCHAR(50),
    color VARCHAR(50),
    weight DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE usage_tracking (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    item_id INT NOT NULL,
    user_id INT NOT NULL,
    check_out_date DATE NOT NULL,
    check_in_date DATE
);
